OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782485286
OL,3,CSecond man arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after summer solstice death
OL,6,FA second man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after the death of
OL,8,Fa man at a summer solstice event.
OL,10,FDerbyshire Police were called to
OL,11,Freports of a man's body being found at
OL,12,FNine Ladies Stone Circle in Stanton
OL,13,FLees at 1.38pm on Monday 22 June.
OL,15,FIsaac Clare-Watts was declared dead at
OL,16,Fthe scene.
OL,18,FInvestigations into the circumstances
OL,19,Fsurrounding the 26-year-old's death
OL,20,Fare ongoing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
