OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782485286
OL,3,CSecond man arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after summer solstice death
OL,6,FA 23-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,FThursday 25 June on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmurder and remains in custody.
OL,10,FA 41-year-old man who had been
OL,11,Farrested on suspicion of murder has
OL,12,Fbeen released on bail as
OL,13,Finvestigations continue.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
