OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782485286
OL,3,CSecond man arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after summer solstice death
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Tony Owen, from
OL,7,Fthe East Midlands Special Operations
OL,8,FUnit (EMSOU), who is leading the
OL,9,Finvestigation, said previously: "I am
OL,10,Furgently appealing for anyone who
OL,11,Fattended the summer solstice event
OL,12,Fover the weekend to please speak to
OL,13,Fofficers as soon as they can.
OL,15,F"A young man's life has been taken in
OL,16,Fthe most brutal way so it is vital
OL,17,Fthat myself and the team build up a
OL,18,Fclear picture of the exact
OL,19,Fcircumstances surrounding his death.
OL,26,@qD@aOUwD@AOU
